OL,3,CAndy Carroll denies breaching court
OL,4,Corder against ex-wife
OL,6,FThe ex-Newcastle United, Liverpool and
OL,7,FWest Ham striker Andy Carroll has
OL,8,Fpleaded not guilty to a charge of
OL,9,Fbreaching a non-molestation order.
OL,11,FMr Carroll, 37, is accused of
OL,12,Fbreaching an order made by the family
OL,13,Fcourt at Chelmsford Justice Centre by
OL,14,Fallegedly repeatedly calling his ex-
OL,15,Fwife Ms Mucklow "without reasonable
OL,16,Fexcuse" in March last year.
OL,18,FA trial date of January 18, 2027 was
OL,19,Fset at a hearing at Chelmsford Crown
OL,20,FCourt on Tuesday and Carroll formally
OL,21,Fentered his plea on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/4
