OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1772831518
OL,3,CAndy Carroll denies breaching court
OL,4,Corder against ex-wife
OL,6,FHe began his professional career with
OL,7,FNewcastle United before transferring
OL,8,Fto Liverpool for #35 million in 2011,
OL,9,Flater playing for West Ham, Reading
OL,10,Fand West Brom among other teams.
OL,12,FCarroll did not attend Tuesday's
OL,13,Fhearing, with those representing him
OL,14,Fbelieving the hearing was taking place
OL,15,Fon Wednesday.
OL,17,FAs a result, the judge adjourned
OL,18,FCarroll's arraignment by one day until
OL,19,FWednesday when he entered his plea of
OL,20,Fnot guilty.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
