FL,426,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1772831518
OL,3,CAndy Carroll denies breaching court
OL,4,Corder against ex-wife
OL,6,FCarroll answered "yes" to confirm his
OL,7,Fname and said "not guilty" when asked
OL,8,Ffor his plea.
OL,10,FProsecutor Philippa Page said there
OL,11,Fhad been "some mix-up regarding the
OL,12,Fdates for the plea and trial
OL,13,Fpreparation hearing, so Mr Carroll and
OL,14,Fhis legal team didn't appear
OL,15,Fyesterday".
OL,17,FAfter Carroll formally entered his
OL,18,Fplea, Judge Mary Loram KC told him:
OL,19,F"I'm adjourning your case for trial on
OL,20,FJanuary 18 next year."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/4
