PN,42504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F425A1772831518
OL,3,CAndy Carroll denies breaching court
OL,4,Corder against ex-wife
OL,6,FCarroll, who currently plays for
OL,7,FNational League South club Dagenham &
OL,8,FRedbridge, played nine matches for
OL,9,FEngland between 2010 and 2012, scoring
OL,10,Ftwice, including one goal at Euro 2012.
OL,12,FThe judge granted Carroll bail and at
OL,13,Fthe end of the hearing he said "thank
OL,14,Fyou, thanks".
